reviewText: This is a really good movie to watch and i want every one to know it. I told all my friends about it and they love it buy this movie or you won't be missing out.
This movie was well thought out, and the writer and acting was good. The package was good came on time. Me and my friends loved the movie. I would give this a 8 out of 10 stars.
